  "author": "Guru Bin",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "macroAmpullae=1.0: maximum touch sensitivity across all expression simultaneously. LFO1 sweeps HAMMER slowly at 0.07 Hz. breathRate=0.067 Hz (physiological breathing). Every keystroke reveals the full dynamic range of the engine — soft touches produce barely-there wisps; hard strikes produce full HAMMER interaction. The hammerhead's ampullae of Lorenzini detect the faintest electrical field. At maximum, no expression is wasted.",
  "tags": ["ouie", "ampullae", "expression", "touch-sensitivity", "breath", "lfo-hammer", "aether", "velocity", "dynamic"],
  "tier": "transcendental",
  "guru_bin": {
    "retreat": "OUIE — The Hammerhead",
    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "vol": "Transcendental Vol 1",
    "scripture": [
      "The ampullae of Lorenzini detect what no eye can see.",
      "At AMPULLAE=1.0, the engine hears the electricity of your intent, not just your finger.",
      "Every gesture is a parameter change. Play accordingly."
    ],
    "revelation": null,
    "god": null,
    "flock_note": "This preset rewards slow, intentional playing. Fast aggressive playing will be overwhelming — the maximum touch sensitivity amplifies everything. Pairs exceptionally well with a keyboard velocity curve set to linear. Try on synth pads at pianissimo: notes will emerge and dissolve at the threshold of hearing.",
    "diagnosis": "The definitive AMPULLAE demonstration. VA+FM pairing is intentionally broad-spectrum so the velocity expression is clearly audible across all registers. LFO1 at 0.07 Hz (slightly faster than breath) creates a slowly shifting HAMMER context that velocity riding discovers differently each note. High unison detune (0.18) adds movement that velocity reveals at forte but conceals at piano."
  },
